            </span>
            <h3>Ideal Relationship</h3>
            <p>We match you with people whose values, goals, and energy actually align with yours.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature reveal">
            <span class="feature__icon" style="--bg: linear-gradient(135deg,#A78BFA,#fd297b)">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="white" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 12c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8s-8 3.58-8 8c0 1.39.36 2.7 1 3.83V20l3.5-1.5c1.07.32 2.21.5 3.5.5 4.42 0 8-3.58 8-8z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Dating With Benefits</h3>
            <p>Real-time chat, voice and video calls, GIFs and reactions — keep the spark alive once you match.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="feature reveal">
            <span class="feature__icon" style="--bg: linear-gradient(135deg,#22C55E,#3B82F6)">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" fill="white" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a5 5 0 0 1 5 5c0 2.76-2.24 5-5 5S7 9.76 7 7a5 5 0 0 1 5-5zm0 12c4.42 0 8 1.79 8 4v4H4v-4c0-2.21 3.58-4 8-4z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Date Beautiful People</h3>
            <p>Every profile is real and verified. No bots, no catfish. Just people actually looking for what you are.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       SMART MATCH
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="smart" id="smartmatch">
    <h2 class="section-title smart__title reveal">Chat &amp; Smart Match</h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal">
      Music tastes, watch lists, hobbies — Spark surfaces what you have in common with every match so the conversation starts itself.
    </p>

    <div class="smart__stage reveal">
      <div class="smart__phone smart__phone--left" data-parallax="0.1">
        <div class="smart__avatar smart__avatar--a"></div>
        <div class="smart__chip smart__chip--spotify">
          <span class="smart__chip-dot" style="background:#1DB954"></span>
          <strong>Spotify</strong>
          <em>14 common songs</em>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="smart__hearts" id="smart-hearts" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="smart__phone smart__phone--right" data-parallax="-0.1">
        <div class="smart__avatar smart__avatar--b"></div>
        <div class="smart__chip smart__chip--netflix">
          <span class="smart__chip-dot" style="background:#E50914"></span>
          <strong>Netflix</strong>
          <em>4 common shows</em>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="smart__clouds" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       VERIFIED + DOWNLOAD — replace href once App Store + Play
       Store URLs are live.
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="verified" id="download">
    <div class="verified__inner">
      <div class="verified__copy">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">
          Only Real Verified Profiles Are Allowed To Join <span class="verified__check">✓</span>
